dc_description_s: This line shapefile represents the boundary lines of the states of the United States at 1:100,000 scale. This layer is part of the 2014 ESRI Data and Maps collection for ArcGIS 10.2.U.S. State Boundaries provides detailed boundary lines consistent with the state, block group, tract, and county data sets and are effective for cartographic display at regional and state levels.
